title: My other websites/Tumblr news
body:
So in case most of you didn’t know, it seems like Tumblr has finally had their say regarding NSFW stuff on their site:

https://staff.tumblr.com/post/180758987165/a-better-more-positive-tumblr

So if this is true, This is blog will no longer exist on Dec. 17, unless I do something to stop that, soooo……

I’ll be making an effort to rid some of the nsfw stuff on there and remain active.(unless I miss something and the blog gets deleted anyways)

However I have my other art sites here that still contain much of my NSFW stuff

http://www.furaffinity.net/user/howsplendid/
https://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=5406515
https://howsplendid.newgrounds.com/
https://www.instagram.com/isaac_yep/?hl=en
https://ko-fi.com/howsplendid
https://www.patreon.com/HowSplendid

https://inkbunny.net/HowSplendid

https://twitter.com/H0wSplendid

https://twitter.com/Quite5plendid (NSFW)

For those of you who have been loyal to the page for the years, I would love to have your continued support on my other sites. Please click on any of the links above! They most of them will still contain the same nsfw stuff I’ve done on there.

Thanks a lot guys, hope to see you all there.^^



*EDIT had to repost because my twitter links weren’t working. They should be good now. thanks
